<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>DomeSso</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body class="<%= set_theme %>">
<div id="top" class="top container-fluid">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="left-menu">
      主站
      <span class="caret"></span>
      <ul class="hover-menu">
        <li>
          <a href="http://www.domelab.com">Domelab</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="http://www.robodou.cn">Robodou</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="right-menu">
      <ul class="horizontal-ul">
        <li>
          <a href="https://intro.domelab.com/">关于我们</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="">CN</a>
        </li>
        <% if cookies[:tgt] %>
        <li><%= link_to("登出", "/logout") %></li>
        <% else %>
          <% if params[:service].present? %>
            <% addon = URI.encode_www_form("service"=>params[:service]) %>
              <li><%= link_to("注册", "/users/new?"+addon) %></li>
              <li><%= link_to("登录", "/login?"+addon) %></li>
            <% else %>
              <li><%= link_to("注册", "/users/new") %></li>
              <li><%= link_to("登录", "/login") %></li>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<% flash.each do |key, value| %>
    <div class="alert">
      <span class="<%= key %>"><%= value %></span>
    </div>
<% end %>
<div id="yield">
  <%= yield %>
</div>
<div id="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="title">
      我们是谁？
    </div>
    <div class="left">
      <div class="con">
        dome机器人学习器材是一个包含金属积木、子模块、软件工具等几百种零件的工程积木平台。dome机器人学习器材是一个包含金属....................................
      </div>
      <div class="link">
        <a href="">（查看详情）</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="middle">
      <p>联系方式</p>

      <p>电话：021-31653316</p>

      <p>邮箱：service@robodou.cn</p>

      <p>地址：上海市钦州北路68号B3栋101室</p>
    </div>
    <div class="right">
      <div class="QR">
        <img src="<%= image_path('QRcode.png') %>" alt=""/>
      </div>
      <div class="QR    ">
        <img src="<%= image_path('QRcode.png') %>" alt=""/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!--<%= debug(params) if Rails.env.development? %>-->
<div class="loading hidden">
</div>
</body>
</html>
